  "It quadruples": "",
  "It doubles": "",
  "It stays the same": "",
  "It halves": "",
  "F_c = mv²/r. Since F_c ∝ v², doubling v makes F_c four times as large.": "",
  "What is the role of the normal force in circular motion on a vertical loop?": "",
  "It is always equal to the weight": "",
